description: GreenBank Capital Inc., through its subsidiaries, invests in small cap businesses in North America. It operates through three segments: Investment, Software Development, and Mineral Exploration. The company provides public listings, pre-IPO funding, private equity, merger and acquisitions, reverse mergers, business incubating, corporate restructuring, and liquidity provision services, as well as stock transfer agency services. It also develops blockchain based apps and mobile application games, as well as engages in the mineral exploration activities. GreenBank Capital Inc. was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
